t's a nice day today, isn't it~?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"bye01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-001","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"Ah, Marina-san, {{userName}}, hi.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-002","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"Were you looking at something on your phone? Did we interrupt you?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"No, it's okay. I was watching footage from the concert we had the other day.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"Oh. Is it a show you played at a different live house?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"Umm, no, it was a concert we held with the help of our school's first and second-year students.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"Wow~. So it was like a farewell concert?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"Well, something like that. Kasumi and Tsurumaki-san said they wanted to do something for the seniors who are graduating...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"At first, I was worried about how to hold the concert, but then, things just kind of took shape.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"I was relieved to hear that the seniors really liked it.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"I see. So, what kind of concert was it actually?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"We decided to livestream the show so even the seniors who weren't coming to school could see it.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"And then Okusawa-san said we should archive it too. That way, seniors busy with exams could watch it whenever they wanted to.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"Ah, good point! That was a great idea. If the concert is saved somewhere, even people who saw it on the day it was held can watch it again later.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"But why were you and Misaki-chan organizing it?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"surprised01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"It all started with something Kasumi and Tsurumaki-san said, and then it naturally fell on us two...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"smile03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"Those two really put us in a tough spot. They just said things, but we were the ones who had to put it together.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"Fufu.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"It's nothing to laugh at.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"sad01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"I'm sorry. It's just that, you try to sound annoyed, but you and Misaki-chan don't mind it when things like that happen, do you?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"smile03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"Be honest with me.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"Ugh... W-well, I wanted to cheer up the seniors too, so I'm glad they were happy with how things turned out.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"odoodo01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"Fufu, it's exactly because you're that way that everyone loves you so much.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"Huh? L-love? What do you mean...?!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"shame01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"Well, you made it through a year of student council, right? I'm sure that was because everyone loves you and wants to work together with you.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":201,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"Arisa","body":"Well, um... I don't know about that...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"odoodo01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"ev213-me1-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":201}],"windowDisplayName":"Marina","body":"By the way, are you going to stick with student council for another year?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":201,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timin